{'id': 19658292, 'body': "This is definitely not the experience we want you to have. Let's get this figured out! Please email us at appreview@varomoney.com so we can identify your account and ensure that you get access to your funds. If you are unable to transfer funds using an external bank account, we may have several options we can look into so you can access your funds quickly if you do not have your Varo debit card. 

Please also ensure that your app is up to date if you are experiencing any bugs or issues with the mobile app. If the problem persists, please let us know and we can have our engineer team investigate further. In the meantime, you can always access your Varo Bank account information through our website. 

